ss=\"why-num\">02<\/div>\n      <div class=\"why-icon\">🚀<\/div>\n      <div class=\"why-name\">Fast Local Delivery<\/div>\n      <p class=\"why-desc\">Based in Lebanon, shipping to Lebanon. Free delivery on every order, to every corner of the country.<\/p>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"why-item reveal d2\">\n      <div class=\"why-num\">03<\/div>\n      <div class=\"why-icon\">🛡️<\/div>\n      <div class=\"why-name\">100% Authentic<\/div>\n      <p class=\"why-desc\">We only carry genuine products. What you see is what you get — no fakes, no compromises, ever.<\/p>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n<!-- REVIEWS -->\n<section class=\"reviews-section\">\n  <div class=\"reviews-header reveal\">\n    <div>\n      <span class=\"section-label\">Real Reviews<\/span>\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">What our girls<br><em>are saying<\/em><\/h2>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"rating-summary\">\n      <div class=\"rating-big\">4.9<\/div>\n      <div class=\"rating-stars\">★★★★★<\/div>\n      <div class=\"rating-count\">10,000+ verified reviews<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n  <div class=\"reviews-grid\">\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <div class=\"review-quote\">\"<\/div>\n      <div class=\"review-stars\">★★★★★<\/div>\n      <p class=\"review-text\">I've tried every eyeliner tool out there. This stamp is genuinely different — my wings come out identical every single morning. I've recommended it to literally everyone I know.<\/p>\n      <div class=\"review-footer\">\n        <div class=\"review-avatar\">S<\/div>\n        <div><div class=\"review-name\">Sara M.<\/div><div class=\"review-meta\">Eyeliner Stamp · Beirut<\/div><\/div>\n        <span class=\"verified\">✓ Verified<\/span>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <div class=\"review-quote\">\"<\/div>\n      <div class=\"review-stars\">★★★★★<\/div>\n      <p class=\"review-text\">The Turmeric Glow Bar actually works. My skin looks brighter after just a week. The formula is so gentle and smells amazing. A permanent part of my routine now.<\/p>\n      <div class=\"review-footer\">\n        <div class=\"review-avatar\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#E8D5A8,#C9A96E)\">L<\/div>\n        <div><div class=\"review-name\">Lara K.<\/div><div class=\"review-meta\">Turmeric Glow Bar · Tripoli<\/div><\/div>\n        <span class=\"verified\">✓ Verified<\/span>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <div class=\"review-quote\">\"<\/div>\n      <div class=\"review-stars\">★★★★★<\/div>\n      <p class=\"review-text\">The Freckles Pen is so realistic — people keep asking if they're real! Delivery was super fast too. Jolie is the only beauty store I fully trust now.<\/p>\n      <div class=\"review-footer\">\n        <div class=\"review-avatar\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#D8C8E8,#9070B8)\">N<\/div>\n        <div><div class=\"review-name\">Nour H.<\/div><div class=\"review-meta\">Freckles Pen · Jounieh<\/div><\/div>\n        <span class=\"verified\">✓ Verified<\/span>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n<!-- NEWSLETTER -->\n<section class=\"nl-section\">\n  <div class=\"nl-info reveal\">\n    <span class=\"section-label\">Stay in the Loop<\/span>\n    <h2 class=\"section-title\">Exclusive deals,<br><em>first access.<\/em><\/h2>\n    <p>Join the Jolie community and be first to know about new arrivals, flash sales, and beauty tips.<\/p>\n    <div class=\"nl-perks\">\n      <div class=\"perk\"><div class=\"perk-check\">✓<\/div>Early access to new products<\/div>\n      <div class=\"perk\"><div class=\"perk-check\">✓<\/div>Exclusive member-only discounts<\/div>\n      <div class=\"perk\"><div class=\"perk-check\">✓<\/div>Beauty tips &amp; tutorials<\/div>\n      <div class=\"perk\"><div class=\"perk-check\">✓<\/div>Flash sale alerts<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n  <div class=\"nl-form reveal d1\">\n    <p class=\"nl-eyebrow\">Join Free — No Spam, Ever<\/p>\n    <div class=\"nl-inputs\">\n      <input class=\"nl-input\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Your name\"\/>\n      <input class=\"nl-input\" type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your email address\"\/>\n      <button class=\"nl-btn\">Join the Jolie Community →<\/button>\n    <\/div>\n    <p class=\"nl-note\">Unsubscribe anytime. We respect your inbox.<\/p>\n  <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n<script>\n\/\/ ── Scroll reveal ──\nconst revealObs = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {\n  entries.forEach(e => { if(e.isIntersecting) e.target.classList.add('visible') });\n}, {threshold: 0.1});\ndocument.querySelectorAll('.product-card, .review-card, .reveal').forEach(el => revealObs.observe(el));\n\n\/\/ ── Marquee — guaranteed RAF scroll ──\n(function(){\n  const track = document.getElementById('marqueeTrack');\n  if(!track) return;\n  \/\/ clone once for seamless loop\n  track.innerHTML += track.innerHTML;\n  let x = 0;\n  const speed = 0.55;\n  function tick(){\n    x -= speed;\n    const half = track.scrollWidth \/ 2;\n    if(Math.abs(x) >= half) x = 0;\n    track.style.transform = 'translateX(' + x + 'px)';\n    requestAnimationFrame(tick);\n  }\n  requestAnimationFrame(tick);\n})();\n<\/script>\n<\/body>\n<\/html>","full_width":true,"show_divider":false,"padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}}},"order":["slideshow","featured_collection_TNdH3Y","scrolling_promotion_QtVqFY","scrolling_promotion_gqQrxK","testimonials_RAYR9d","custom_liquid_LWEg3f"]}